title: Melo (Diogo de Azambuja de)
body: This Governor-General of Madeira under the Filipino domain was appointed on May 23, 1594, and took office on January 20, 1595. He died in Funchal in 1600.

1594: Appointment of Diogo de Azambuja de Melo as Governor-General of Madeira
1595: Inauguration of Diogo de Azambuja de Melo as Governor-General of Madeira
1600: Death of Diogo de Azambuja de Melo in Funchal
